00:00:34.920 --> 00:00:36.500
that exist in motivation, those

00:00:36.500 --> 00:00:39.460
techniques of change, modification,

00:00:39.640 --> 00:00:42.760
improvement of motivation.

00:00:42.760 --> 00:00:44.560
And, of course, when we talk

00:00:44.560 --> 00:00:46.800
