00:00:46.800 --> 00:00:48.340
stop at the main problems

00:00:48.340 --> 00:00:50.440
that arise in this

00:00:50.440 --> 00:00:51.400
system.

00:00:51.520 --> 00:00:52.480
If we go to the problems of motivation,

00:00:52.480 --> 00:00:54.260
then this problem, one could say,

00:00:54.260 --> 00:00:55.240
is as old as the world.

00:00:55.820 --> 00:00:57.020
What is motivation?

00:00:57.400 --> 00:00:59.600
If not to get into the various academic

00:00:59.600 --> 00:01:01.100
theories, the disputes which,

00:01:01.100 --> 00:01:02.280
in principle, we are not interested,

00:01:02.280 --> 00:01:03.600
because the challenge that is before

00:01:03.600 --> 00:01:05.380
us is to master those practical

00:01:05.380 --> 00:01:06.980
