00:01:06.980 --> 00:01:08.080
to us from the point of view

00:01:08.080 --> 00:01:10.680
of our functioning in business,

00:01:10.680 --> 00:01:13.240
from the point of view of

00:01:13.240 --> 00:01:14.660
solving those business

00:01:14.660 --> 00:01:16.720
challenges that are before us.

00:01:16.880 --> 00:01:18.660
Therefore, from the point

00:01:18.660 --> 00:01:19.720
of view of pragmatic assessment,

00:01:19.760 --> 00:01:20.840
pragmatic understanding

00:01:20.840 --> 00:01:22.640
of motivation, it represents

00:01:22.640 --> 00:01:25.000
the reasons that determine

00:01:25.000 --> 00:01:26.140
human behavior.

00:01:26.640 --> 00:01:30.020
Why does a man make an

00:01:30.020 --> 00:01:31.300
effort to work?

00:01:31.300 --> 00:01:33.460
Why does he work with an enthusiast,

00:01:33.700 --> 00:01:35.500
or does he work with a coolant?

00:01:36.000 --> 00:01:38.400
Why does a person

00:01:38.400 --> 00:01:39.920
sit late at work to get the

00:01:40.180 --> 00:01:42.060
same results, regardless

00:01:42.060 --> 00:01:44.240
of whether he will receive

00:01:44.240 --> 00:01:45.520
an additional reward

00:01:45.520 --> 00:01:47.700
for this, or not?

00:01:48.020 --> 00:01:52.260
And why a person, even seemingly,

00:01:52.360 --> 00:01:54.360
occupying a certain status position,

00:01:54.360 --> 00:02:00.820
having a good enough fork, and

00:02:01.240 --> 00:02:03.180
work does not cause him to rise,

00:02:03.180 --> 00:02:04.960
does not cause him to interest,

00:02:04.960 --> 00:02:06.920
he is sitting down, serves his

00:02:06.920 --> 00:02:09.780
deadlines, how the attitude of

00:02:09.780 --> 00:02:12.440
a person to work, how this

00:02:12.440 --> 00:02:14.040
attitude passes, because we

00:02:14.040 --> 00:02:17.400
all know that our motivation does

00:02:17.400 --> 00:02:19.280
not remain constant, if we

00:02:19.280 --> 00:02:20.820
face some interesting thing, with

00:02:20.820 --> 00:02:21.940
some interesting problem,

00:02:21.940 --> 00:02:25.240
then we are interested in

00:02:25.240 --> 00:02:28.720
them, we try to find different

00:02:28.720 --> 00:02:30.680
ways, ways of approach,

00:02:30.840 --> 00:02:32.780
to get new knowledge to

00:02:32.900 --> 00:02:34.300
solve the tasks that are

00:02:34.300 --> 00:02:37.680
before us, and we seek results.

00:02:38.120 --> 00:02:39.840
As we these results, our

00:02:39.840 --> 00:02:42.840
interest continues to fall.

00:02:43.180 --> 00:02:45.180
We already know how to solve it.

00:02:45.340 --> 00:02:48.420
It is turning for us from new to

00:02:48.420 --> 00:02:51.360
routine, to usual, to usual, and

00:02:51.560 --> 00:02:54.420
we already know what and how to do.

00:02:54.420 --> 00:02:55.720
We know what difficulties

00:02:55.720 --> 00:02:58.460
will arise when there will be problems

00:02:58.460 --> 00:03:00.280
with reports, and so on.

00:03:01.260 --> 00:03:04.140
And from this rise of the original,

00:03:04.140 --> 00:03:06.560
with which we dealt with this

00:03:06.560 --> 00:03:11.180
problem, we are already moving

00:03:11.180 --> 00:03:13.840
to a calm, or excluded, time-driven.

00:03:14.360 --> 00:03:15.620
The other side of the problem.

00:03:16.140 --> 00:03:18.600
We solve a task.

00:03:18.860 --> 00:03:21.740
For example, we are aiming to increase

00:03:21.740 --> 00:03:23.820
our sales plans within a month

00:03:23.820 --> 00:03:26.340
by 10-15%.

00:03:26.340 --> 00:03:29.140
We solve this task, actively solve

00:03:29.140 --> 00:03:31.260
it, but bonuses are promised for it.

00:03:31.620 --> 00:03:33.260
We were hinted that if we

00:03:33.260 --> 00:03:34.800
deal with this task, we will get

00:03:34.800 --> 00:03:36.220
some career prospects, and we

00:03:36.220 --> 00:03:38.420
will devote all our strength,

00:03:38.420 --> 00:03:41.120
all our efforts to solve

00:03:41.120 --> 00:03:42.280
the problems we face, fine

00:03:42.700 --> 00:03:45.040
opportunities, try to harm

00:03:45.080 --> 00:03:48.380
new schemes, new models, well

00:03:48.720 --> 00:03:49.680
or it works.

00:03:50.380 --> 00:03:54.880
We do not have a steady growth

00:03:54.880 --> 00:03:56.880
in sales, and accordingly

00:03:56.880 --> 00:03:59.700
we begin to understand that we

00:03:59.700 --> 00:04:02.900
will not be able to the result

00:04:02.900 --> 00:04:04.660
at the end of the month, and

00:04:04.660 --> 00:04:06.640
again our motivation

00:04:06.640 --> 00:04:07.840
is falling.

00:04:07.960 --> 00:04:10.120
Only in this case it falls not because

00:04:10.120 --> 00:04:14.000
we have decided on the task and accordingly

00:04:14.000 --> 00:04:16.340
we already know how and what to do,

00:04:16.340 --> 00:04:18.300
it falls precisely because we

00:04:18.300 --> 00:04:20.220
have lowered our hands.

00:04:20.580 --> 00:04:23.480
We realized that we will not

00:04:23.480 --> 00:04:24.360
solve the task.

00:04:25.100 --> 00:04:28.700
We convinced ourselves that it was

00:04:28.700 --> 00:04:30.440
mid-month today, and I have a sales

00:04:30.440 --> 00:04:33.280
growth of only three percent.

00:04:34.360 --> 00:04:36.720
And so, we have been scheduled

00:04:36.720 --> 00:04:38.700
in our own defeat, so we lose the motive,

00:04:38.700 --> 00:04:40.980
we lose the cause of behavior, we

00:04:40.980 --> 00:04:42.140
have decided for ourselves,

00:04:42.140 --> 00:04:45.040
we will not cope with the task.

00:04:45.600 --> 00:04:48.340
And so we are also starting

00:04:48.340 --> 00:04:50.100
to work again, already realizing that

00:04:50.540 --> 00:04:54.060
at the end of the month we will

00:04:54.060 --> 00:04:55.700
have to report why the task

00:04:55.700 --> 00:04:56.860
is not solved.

00:04:56.860 --> 00:04:58.500
It is also a problem of motivation.

00:04:58.800 --> 00:05:01.820
How to such a situation?

00:05:01.900 --> 00:05:04.640
Such a situation that a person is

00:05:04.640 --> 00:05:07.120
not afraid to make a mistake,

00:05:07.120 --> 00:05:11.600
that a person understands that

00:05:11.600 --> 00:05:14.240
if he solves a new task, it does

00:05:14.360 --> 00:05:15.520
not mean that he will necessarily

00:05:15.520 --> 00:05:17.160
get it right away.

00:05:18.140 --> 00:05:20.240
Here there are old problems of the

00:05:20.240 --> 00:05:22.100
ratio of my responsibility, the delegation

00:05:22.200 --> 00:05:24.340
of responsibility to me, the problem

00:05:24.920 --> 00:05:27.800
of counting the results obtained.

00:05:27.880 --> 00:05:32.060
The problem of finding the balance between

00:05:32.060 --> 00:05:33.980
freedom and dependence.

00:05:34.480 --> 00:05:37.740
Freedom to delegate any other powers.

00:05:38.000 --> 00:05:40.580
This is all that large, colossal

00:05:40.580 --> 00:05:42.300
topic that is related to the issues

00:05:42.300 --> 00:05:43.660
of motivation.

00:05:44.240 --> 00:05:45.380
And accordingly, this is the

00:05:45.560 --> 00:05:47.900
topic that arises before us

00:05:47.900 --> 00:05:51.460
every day during our business work.

00:05:51.500 --> 00:05:54.280
We can motivate ourselves, we want

00:05:54.280 --> 00:05:56.460
to go to work, we want to develop,

00:05:56.460 --> 00:05:58.000
we don’t want to develop in terms

00:05:58.000 --> 00:05:59.660
of the development of the company,

00:05:59.660 --> 00:06:01.400
the development of business.

00:06:01.540 --> 00:06:03.060
We are obliged to motivate

00:06:03.060 --> 00:06:05.480
employees if we are the managers

00:06:05.480 --> 00:06:07.580
of the business owner, because

00:06:07.580 --> 00:06:09.720
it is the employees that are

00:06:09.720 --> 00:06:11.080
the tool, the way in which

00:06:11.260 --> 00:06:13.320
we get the desired results

00:06:13.320 --> 00:06:15.640
for us, but here it is very

00:06:15.640 --> 00:06:17.560
important to understand that

00:06:17.680 --> 00:06:21.080
people, staff, colleagues should

00:06:21.160 --> 00:06:22.740
not be seen as a means

00:06:22.740 --> 00:06:24.240
to their goals.

00:06:24.620 --> 00:06:26.440
People feel this very well,

00:06:26.440 --> 00:06:27.620
and it is a huge

00:06:27.620 --> 00:06:29.820
demotory factor.

00:06:31.320 --> 00:06:33.580
The problem of human resource management

00:06:33.580 --> 00:06:34.780
in terms of building a

00:06:34.780 --> 00:06:36.960
motivation system is also a very

00:06:36.960 --> 00:06:38.060
interesting problem, which

00:06:38.060 --> 00:06:39.900
we will pay a lot of attention

00:06:39.900 --> 00:06:41.400
to today.

00:06:42.500 --> 00:06:46.180
Well, of course, the basic term

00:06:46.200 --> 00:06:48.220
that interests us is what

00:06:48.220 --> 00:06:50.740
is work motivation?

00:06:51.140 --> 00:06:54.080
Motivation is a general concept

00:06:54.080 --> 00:06:57.560
associated with the search for causes

00:06:57.560 --> 00:06:59.260
of human behavior.

00:06:59.980 --> 00:07:03.540
But when we talk about commerce, about

00:07:03.540 --> 00:07:05.680
business, we are not interested

00:07:05.680 --> 00:07:07.860
in human behavior at all.

00:07:08.320 --> 00:07:10.820
This is an interesting academic

00:07:11.000 --> 00:07:12.680
topic that scientists can engage

00:07:12.900 --> 00:07:15.360
in, but we are interested in

00:07:15.360 --> 00:07:17.020
the specific reason for the

00:07:17.140 --> 00:07:19.020
behavior of a person in

00:07:19.020 --> 00:07:20.940
the implementation of his work

00:07:21.280 --> 00:07:24.320
activity, his functional duties

00:07:24.320 --> 00:07:25.740
that are related to the

00:07:25.740 --> 00:07:27.520
work that Auna performs, the

00:07:27.520 --> 00:07:28.320
work for which he

00:07:28.320 --> 00:07:31.040
is rewarded, and the work

00:07:31.080 --> 00:07:33.200
that in principle interests us,

00:07:33.400 --> 00:07:34.840
the work that we organize.

00:07:35.020 --> 00:07:39.320
Again, we will not give different arguments

00:07:39.320 --> 00:07:42.200
in different nuances and subtleties,

00:07:42.380 --> 00:07:44.080
the concepts of labor motivation, because

00:07:44.080 --> 00:07:45.800
If we look at literature, if we look

00:07:46.180 --> 00:07:48.020
at basic fundamental textbooks,

00:07:48.020 --> 00:07:50.620
then accordingly we will

00:07:50.620 --> 00:07:52.780
find different reviews and

00:07:52.780 --> 00:07:55.520
different definitions in them.

00:07:56.400 --> 00:07:58.700
But since we are further

00:07:58.700 --> 00:08:00.500
interested in the practical

00:08:00.500 --> 00:08:02.940
definition, the definition

00:08:03.260 --> 00:08:05.780
that we can use in practice,

00:08:05.780 --> 00:08:08.320
let us under labor motivation

00:08:08.320 --> 00:08:10.020
Under any circumstances,

00:08:10.020 --> 00:08:14.940
during our course, understand

00:08:14.940 --> 00:08:18.740
the process of stimulating,

00:08:18.820 --> 00:08:21.580
first, a single executor, one

00:08:21.700 --> 00:08:25.040
employee, or the entire

00:08:25.040 --> 00:08:26.640
labor team.

00:08:26.680 --> 00:08:27.780
Moreover, this stimulation

00:08:27.780 --> 00:08:29.860
process is aimed at achieving

00:08:29.860 --> 00:08:32.260
the specific goals that are

00:08:32.460 --> 00:08:35.380
faced by the organization, first,

00:08:35.580 --> 00:08:37.660
at achieving these goals, and

00:08:37.660 --> 00:08:40.340
secondly, productive implementation

00:08:40.340 --> 00:08:41.940
of the decisions made and

00:08:41.940 --> 00:08:42.880
planned plans.

00:08:43.820 --> 00:08:46.620
This is a general definition

00:08:47.140 --> 00:08:49.800
that includes an individual employee,

00:08:49.800 --> 00:08:53.360
an entire organization with

00:08:53.360 --> 00:08:55.600
all its characteristics, with

00:08:55.600 --> 00:08:58.280
all its features, with its

00:08:58.280 --> 00:09:00.320
psychological climate, and which

00:09:00.320 --> 00:09:01.540
necessarily includes the

00:09:01.540 --> 00:09:02.980
end result.

00:09:03.460 --> 00:09:06.960
When we talk about business,

00:09:06.960 --> 00:09:09.520
we are primarily interested in

00:09:09.520 --> 00:09:10.340
the final result.

00:09:10.680 --> 00:09:13.300
We invest money and ultimately we

00:09:13.300 --> 00:09:15.300
want to get a return.

00:09:15.620 --> 00:09:16.680
Therefore, we need the final

00:09:16.680 --> 00:09:21.760
result in terms of making certain decisions,

00:09:21.760 --> 00:09:23.220
their achievement, but also

00:09:23.220 --> 00:09:25.260
in terms of realizing the goals,

00:09:25.260 --> 00:09:27.280
missions, tasks, organization

00:09:27.640 --> 00:09:29.100
of the firm in the company

00:09:29.100 --> 00:09:30.260
in which we work.

00:09:30.260 --> 00:09:33.320
These are the aspects that are

00:09:33.320 --> 00:09:35.120
considered, evaluated,

00:09:35.120 --> 00:09:37.120
studied in different

00:09:37.300 --> 00:09:41.040
approaches to motivation.

00:09:42.980 --> 00:09:45.860
Even if we talk about motivation,

00:09:45.860 --> 00:09:50.660
motivation is always related to needs.

00:09:52.200 --> 00:09:53.640
As for needs, again, here it

00:09:53.760 --> 00:09:55.880
should be remembered that business

00:09:56.400 --> 00:09:59.240
needs are understood slightly

00:09:59.240 --> 00:10:01.180
differently than in psychology

00:10:01.180 --> 00:10:04.040
or academic environments.

00:10:04.540 --> 00:10:06.400
In psychology, well, in life in general,

00:10:06.620 --> 00:10:10.440
a need is a need of a person for something.

00:10:10.600 --> 00:10:12.260
Man lacks something.

00:10:12.280 --> 00:10:14.540
He wants to eat, drink,

00:10:15.120 --> 00:10:16.900
rest, walk, enjoy.

00:10:17.760 --> 00:10:19.100
And, accordingly, it

00:10:19.100 --> 00:10:20.920
makes efforts to meet

00:10:20.920 --> 00:10:22.740
these needs.

00:10:23.940 --> 00:10:26.340
As for business, of course there

00:10:26.340 --> 00:10:28.880
is a need for something here too,

00:10:28.880 --> 00:10:31.900
but this is already a specific

00:10:31.900 --> 00:10:34.580
need, a need to and receive

00:10:34.580 --> 00:10:37.260
profit, a need to establish

00:10:37.260 --> 00:10:40.800
contractual relations with employees,

00:10:40.800 --> 00:10:44.760
contractual relations with

00:10:44.760 --> 00:10:48.160
partners, with those people

00:10:48.160 --> 00:10:51.420
who are bound to us, with whom

00:10:51.420 --> 00:10:53.600
we have common rules and

00:10:53.600 --> 00:10:55.120
principles of work.

00:10:55.460 --> 00:10:59.540
There are two types

00:10:59.540 --> 00:11:02.060
of needs: primary

00:11:02.060 --> 00:11:06.200
and secondary.

00:11:06.200 --> 00:11:10.660
The primary needs are those

00:11:10.660 --> 00:11:13.480
that are necessary for

00:11:13.480 --> 00:11:16.080
a person to be able

00:11:16.080 --> 00:11:18.080
to work.

00:11:19.380 --> 00:11:20.600
In order for a man to work,

00:11:20.640 --> 00:11:21.860
he must be full.

00:11:21.860 --> 00:11:23.340
Because if you sit at work

00:11:23.340 --> 00:11:26.040
hungry, you will think first

00:11:26.220 --> 00:11:27.600
of all not about doing

00:11:27.600 --> 00:11:29.340
the job, but about just

00:11:29.340 --> 00:11:31.060
filling your hunger.

00:11:31.500 --> 00:11:36.900
If you sit at work, for example, as

00:11:36.900 --> 00:11:39.420
it is usually in the summer, it is very

00:11:39.560 --> 00:11:41.140
hot outside, and there is no

00:11:41.140 --> 00:11:44.060
air conditioning in the room, then,

00:11:44.140 --> 00:11:46.680
accordingly, you are not thinking

00:11:46.680 --> 00:11:48.500
about working, but you are thinking

00:11:48.500 --> 00:11:50.720
about what to breathe.

00:11:50.820 --> 00:11:52.180
You think about where you would

00:11:52.180 --> 00:11:53.740
drink the same cold water.

00:11:54.640 --> 00:11:57.080
You think that all the windows are on the

00:11:57.080 --> 00:12:00.640
doorstep, and still it is impossible to work.

00:12:01.220 --> 00:12:02.820
Therefore, the primary needs are essentially

00:12:02.820 --> 00:12:05.040
the creation of the conditions

00:12:05.040 --> 00:12:06.680
necessary for work.

00:12:08.680 --> 00:12:10.500
It is the satisfaction of

00:12:10.500 --> 00:12:11.860
the same physiological needs.

00:12:11.880 --> 00:12:14.200
In order for a person to start solving

00:12:14.200 --> 00:12:16.800
business tasks, those necessary

00:12:16.800 --> 00:12:19.940
start needs must only be met

00:12:19.940 --> 00:12:23.340
after the satisfaction of the

00:12:23.340 --> 00:12:25.440
saturation of which he can start

00:12:25.440 --> 00:12:28.440
thinking about something else.

00:12:28.440 --> 00:12:31.300
The other is secondary needs.

00:12:31.420 --> 00:12:33.080
Secondary needs are created in the

00:12:33.080 --> 00:12:36.280
course of life, in the process

00:12:36.280 --> 00:12:39.660
of acquiring experience, in the

00:12:39.660 --> 00:12:42.460
process of acquiring knowledge.

00:12:42.460 --> 00:12:44.180
And, accordingly, secondary

00:12:44.180 --> 00:12:46.680
needs are the needs in achieving

00:12:46.680 --> 00:12:49.940
goals, in obtaining a certain

00:12:49.940 --> 00:12:51.140
status, in career

00:12:51.140 --> 00:12:53.100
growth, in material

00:12:53.100 --> 00:12:57.300
growth, in promotion,

00:12:57.300 --> 00:12:58.920
in getting into the staff

00:12:58.920 --> 00:13:00.300
and so on.

00:13:00.500 --> 00:13:01.840
Only after the primary

00:13:01.840 --> 00:13:03.180
needs are met can

00:13:03.180 --> 00:13:05.400
we talk about secondary needs.

00:13:05.940 --> 00:13:07.280
There are no miracles.

00:13:07.280 --> 00:13:12.260
